      "content": "Students will brainstorm and share common superstitions they know from their own cultures.  This can be done individually, then in pairs, and finally as a whole class.",
      "questions": [
        "What are some common superstitions in your culture?",
        "Do you believe in any superstitions? Why or why not?"
