            "He will give you a magical gift.",
            "He will grant you three wishes.",
            "He will reveal the location of his gold.",
            "He will turn you into a frog."
          ],
          "answer": "He will reveal the location of his gold.",
          "explanation": "The text mentions that a caught leprechaun will reveal the location of his hidden treasure."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sentences",
      "title": "Sentence Frames",
      "frames": [
        {
          "pattern": "I think _____ because _____.",
          "examples": [
            "I think leprechauns are fascinating because of their connection to Irish folklore.",
            "I think the legend of the leprechaun is popular because it involves hidden treasure."
          ],
          "grammarFocus": "Expressing opinions"
        },
        {
          "pattern": "According to the legend, _____.",
          "examples": [
            "According to the legend, leprechauns are excellent shoemakers.",
            "According to the legend, finding a leprechaun's gold is very difficult."
          ],
          "grammarFocus": "Reporting information from a source"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "discussion",
      "title": "Discussion: Superstitions and Beliefs",
